<subSubSection lastPageId="1" lastPageNumber="66" pageId="0" pageNumber="65" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="0.[151,1436,1596,2002]" pageId="0" pageNumber="65">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,338,1667,1691]" pageId="0" pageNumber="65">Description.</emphasis>
Male, total length 7.0. Carapace 
<number box="[688,735,1667,1690]" pageId="0" pageNumber="65" value="4.25">4.25</number>
long, 
<number box="[801,848,1667,1690]" pageId="0" pageNumber="65" value="3.55">3.55</number>
wide, fovea straight, transverse 
<number box="[1190,1237,1667,1690]" pageId="0" pageNumber="65" value="0.57">0.57</number>
wide; brown, with black eye area, dark brown cephalic part and dark-brown chevrons (
<figureCitation box="[885,949,1701,1724]" captionStart="FIGURES 1 – 6" captionStartId="1.[151,269,1978,2002]" captionTargetBox="[196,1389,607,1964]" captionTargetId="figure@1.[195,1392,607,1964]" captionTargetPageId="1" captionText="FIGURES 1 – 6. Somatic characters. 1 &amp; 2 — habitus, in alcohol and dry specimen; 3 — cephalic part, dorsal; 4 — prosoma, ventral; 5 — tibia I, prolateral; 6 — tibia I, ventral." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/277333/files/figure.png" pageId="0" pageNumber="65">
Fig. 
<number box="[936,949,1701,1724]" pageId="0" pageNumber="65" value="3.0">3</number>
</figureCitation>
) and radial stripes; margins of carapace with strong spiniform bristles (
<figureCitation box="[431,496,1736,1759]" captionStart="FIGURES 1 – 6" captionStartId="1.[151,269,1978,2002]" captionTargetBox="[196,1389,607,1964]" captionTargetId="figure@1.[195,1392,607,1964]" captionTargetPageId="1" captionText="FIGURES 1 – 6. Somatic characters. 1 &amp; 2 — habitus, in alcohol and dry specimen; 3 — cephalic part, dorsal; 4 — prosoma, ventral; 5 — tibia I, prolateral; 6 — tibia I, ventral." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/277333/files/figure.png" pageId="0" pageNumber="65">
Fig. 
<number box="[483,496,1736,1759]" pageId="0" pageNumber="65" value="1.0">1</number>
</figureCitation>
). Sternum 
<number box="[619,666,1736,1759]" pageId="0" pageNumber="65" value="2.25">2.25</number>
long, 
<number box="[737,770,1736,1759]" pageId="0" pageNumber="65" value="1.7">1.7</number>
wide, sigilla not evident. Eye sizes and interdistances: AME 
<number box="[151,187,1771,1794]" pageId="0" pageNumber="65" value="0.3">0.3</number>
, ALE 
<number box="[255,304,1771,1794]" pageId="0" pageNumber="65" value="0.27">0.27</number>
, PME 
<number box="[375,424,1771,1794]" pageId="0" pageNumber="65" value="0.14">0.14</number>
, PLE 
<number box="[487,523,1771,1794]" pageId="0" pageNumber="65" value="0.2">0.2</number>
, AME–AME 
<number box="[671,707,1771,1794]" pageId="0" pageNumber="65" value="1.4">1.4</number>
, ALE–ALE 
<number box="[840,889,1771,1794]" pageId="0" pageNumber="65" value="0.66">0.66</number>
, AME–ALE 
<number box="[1030,1079,1771,1794]" pageId="0" pageNumber="65" value="0.16">0.16</number>
, PME–PME 
<number box="[1218,1267,1771,1794]" pageId="0" pageNumber="65" value="0.51">0.51</number>
, PLE–ALE 
<number box="[1396,1432,1771,1794]" pageId="0" pageNumber="65" value="0.2">0.2</number>
, ALE–PLE 0, AME–PME 
<number box="[430,480,1805,1828]" pageId="0" pageNumber="65" value="0.07">0.07</number>
; anterior row– 
<number box="[640,689,1805,1828]" pageId="0" pageNumber="65" value="1.07">1.07</number>
, posterior row – 
<number box="[868,904,1805,1828]" pageId="0" pageNumber="65" value="1.1">1.1</number>
. Chelicera each with 
<number box="[1132,1145,1805,1828]" pageId="0" pageNumber="65" value="7.0">7</number>
large prolateral teeth and 
<number box="[1423,1436,1805,1828]" pageId="0" pageNumber="65" value="5.0">5</number>
fine retrolateral teeth. Maxilla 
<number box="[489,536,1840,1863]" pageId="0" pageNumber="65" value="1.64">1.64</number>
long, 
<number box="[609,656,1840,1863]" pageId="0" pageNumber="65" value="0.64">0.64</number>
wide, cuspules absent. Labium 
<number box="[1011,1058,1840,1863]" pageId="0" pageNumber="65" value="0.29">0.29</number>
long, 
<number box="[1131,1178,1840,1863]" pageId="0" pageNumber="65" value="0.64">0.64</number>
wide, distinct cuspules absent (
<figureCitation box="[234,300,1875,1898]" captionStart="FIGURES 1 – 6" captionStartId="1.[151,269,1978,2002]" captionTargetBox="[196,1389,607,1964]" captionTargetId="figure@1.[195,1392,607,1964]" captionTargetPageId="1" captionText="FIGURES 1 – 6. Somatic characters. 1 &amp; 2 — habitus, in alcohol and dry specimen; 3 — cephalic part, dorsal; 4 — prosoma, ventral; 5 — tibia I, prolateral; 6 — tibia I, ventral." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/277333/files/figure.png" pageId="0" pageNumber="65">
Fig. 
<number box="[284,300,1875,1898]" pageId="0" pageNumber="65" value="4.0">4</number>
</figureCitation>
), but with row of strong setae. Abdomen blackish with 
<number box="[898,911,1875,1898]" pageId="0" pageNumber="65" value="3.0">3</number>
pairs of whitish spots dorsally. Legs long, tibia I with mating spur (megaspine), with 
<number box="[548,561,1909,1932]" pageId="0" pageNumber="65" value="4.0">4</number>
prolateral ventral spines (including megaspine) and 
<number box="[1138,1151,1909,1932]" pageId="0" pageNumber="65" value="4.0">4</number>
retrolateral ventral spines (
<figureCitation box="[158,256,1944,1967]" captionStart="FIGURES 1 – 6" captionStartId="1.[151,269,1978,2002]" captionTargetBox="[196,1389,607,1964]" captionTargetId="figure@1.[195,1392,607,1964]" captionTargetPageId="1" captionText="FIGURES 1 – 6. Somatic characters. 1 &amp; 2 — habitus, in alcohol and dry specimen; 3 — cephalic part, dorsal; 4 — prosoma, ventral; 5 — tibia I, prolateral; 6 — tibia I, ventral." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/277333/files/figure.png" pageId="0" pageNumber="65">
Figs 
<number box="[212,256,1944,1967]" pageId="0" pageNumber="65" value="5.5" valueMax="6.0" valueMin="5.0">5–6</number>
</figureCitation>
). Scopula on tarsi I and II and terminal part of metatarsi I-II. All claws with two rows of teeth; number of teeth vary on different sides, from 
<number box="[461,475,1979,2002]" pageId="0" pageNumber="65" value="4.0">4</number>
- 
<number box="[483,497,1979,2002]" pageId="0" pageNumber="65" value="4.0">4</number>
on leg I, 
<number box="[598,612,1979,2002]" pageId="0" pageNumber="65" value="2.0">2</number>
- 
<number box="[620,634,1979,2002]" pageId="0" pageNumber="65" value="2.0">2</number>
and 
<number box="[685,698,1979,2002]" pageId="0" pageNumber="65" value="3.0">3</number>
- 
<number box="[707,720,1979,2002]" pageId="0" pageNumber="65" value="3.0">3</number>
on legs III–IV respectively.
</paragraph>
